titleInfo.title: Map of tract T-6-S, R-1-E, East Baton Rouge Parish, Louisiana.

mods.abstract: Undated map showing portion of East Baton Rouge Parish from the Blount Road area to the west; to the Comite River on the east. Gives landowners' names and property boundaries. No scale given.
